NIRWAN ANSARI (S'78 M'83 SM'94 F'09)
received the B.S.E.E. (summa cum laude) degree
from the New Jersey Institute of Technology
(NJIT), Newark, NJ, USA, in 1982, the M.S.E.E.
degree from the University of Michigan, Ann
Arbor, MI, USA, in 1983, and the Ph.D. degree
